OL,3,COne in 1,000 people could have gene
OL,4,Cputting them at risk of rare heart
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FA gene which puts people at risk of a
OL,8,Frare and potentially fatal heart
OL,9,Fcondition could be carried by one in
OL,10,F1,000 people, a study has found.
OL,12,FResearchers say the figure is "higher
OL,13,Fthan expected", and while many people
OL,14,Fwon't go on to develop the disease,
OL,15,Fidentifying those who do as early as
OL,16,Fpossible could allow for it to be
OL,17,Ftreated more effectively.
