OL,3,COne in 1,000 people could have gene
OL,4,Cputting them at risk of rare heart
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FCardiac transthyretin (ATTR)
OL,8,Famloidosis happens when the liver
OL,9,Fproduces faulty transthyretin (TTR)
OL,10,Fproteins.
OL,12,FThey can change shape and form clumps
OL,13,Faround the heart, which makes it
OL,14,Fharder for the heart to pump blood and
OL,15,Feventually lead to heart failure.
OL,17,FThe study by University College London
OL,18,F(UCL) and Queen Mary University of
OL,19,FLondon analysed the genes of 469,789
OL,20,Fpeople in the UK.
