OL,3,COne in 1,000 people could have gene
OL,4,Cputting them at risk of rare heart
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FThey found that a hereditary form of
OL,8,Fthe gene is more common in people with
OL,9,Fblack African ancestry and in certain
OL,10,Fpopulations in Portugal, Japan and
OL,11,FSweden, researchers said.
OL,13,FATTR amyloidosis can be caused by a
OL,14,Fmutation in the TTR gene, but can also
OL,15,Fdevelop in people without the mutation.
OL,17,FThe study found about one in 1,000
OL,18,Fpeople had a genetic variant with a
OL,19,Flink to ATTR amyloidosis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
