OL,7,FDr Nay Aung, of the William Harvey
OL,8,FResearch Institute at Queen Mary
OL,9,FUniversity of London, added: "Our
OL,10,Fstudy showed that people carrying
OL,11,Fthese potentially harmful variants
OL,12,Fhave a two-to-three-fold increase in
OL,13,Fthe risk of heart failure and cardiac
OL,14,Frhythm issues.
OL,16,F"This again highlights the need for
OL,17,Fearly detection and monitoring for
OL,18,Fdisease progression."
